                <h1>Lupus Awareness Month: Educate, Advocate, Support</h1>
                <p>Lupus Awareness Month is a crucial time to educate and raise awareness about systemic lupus erythematosus (SLE). SLE affects millions worldwide, often without visible symptoms. This month, join us in sharing stories, supporting research, and advocating for those impacted by lupus. Together, we can promote understanding and care!</p>
